===Noun===
'''kif'''
# a kind of [[cannabis]] smoked in Morocco and Algeria, for [[narcotic]] or [[intoxicating]] effect
#:*'''1882''': I perceived the odour of '''kif''', and recognised the voices of Selam the Second, Abd-el-Rhaman, and others; it was an Arab orgie in full swing. — Edmondo de Amicis, ''Morocco: Its People & Places'', tr. C. Rollin-Tilton